Never used<br>
<br>
LEVEL 40: THE DISCIPLINE OF FEARLESS <br>
Never used<br>
<br>
LEVEL 52: THE DISCIPLINE OF EVASIVE <br>
Havent used since i got 55<br>
<br>
LEVEL 53: THE DISCIPLINE OF CHARGE <br>
One of the best imo. Great damage. Since every swing lands it builds agro as well. Damage multiplying discs dont work well against higher end velious mobs because of their ac, while charge shines. Nice recharge time too.<br>
<br>
LEVEL 54: THE DISCIPLINE OF MIGHTY STRIKE<br>
Rarely used, rather use fellstrike<br>
<br>
LEVEL 55: THE DISCIPLINE OF DEFENSIVE <br>
Rarely used anymore, but against certain mobs.<br>
<br>
LEVEL 56: THE DISCIPLINE OF FURIOUS<br>
Dont use this, fortitude is better<br>
<br>
LEVEL 57: THE DISCIPLINE OF PRECISION <br>
I dont think ive ever used this, might try it out soon.<br>
<br>
LEVEL 58: THE DISCIPLINE OF FELL STRIKE <br>
Simply awesome. Plus the chance of a crippling while berserk make this a fun disc. I like charge better for damage done though.<br>
<br>
LEVEL 59: THE DISCIPLINE OF FORTITUDE<br>
